Description_lang: Your Feral Spirits' attacks have a $s1% chance to trigger Stormbringer, resetting the cooldown of your Stormstrike.

description_blz.en_US: Your Feral Spirits' attacks have a 20% chance to trigger Stormbringer, resetting the cooldown of your Stormstrike.
description_blz.es_MX: Los ataques de tus Espíritus ferales tienen un 20% de probabilidad de activar Portador de tormentas, que restablece el tiempo de reutilización de tu Golpe de tormenta.
description_blz.pt_BR: Seus ataques de Espírito Feral têm 20% de chance de ativar Traztormenta, concluindo a recarga do Ataque da Tempestade.
description_blz.de_DE: Die Angriffe Eurer Wildgeister haben eine Chance von 20%, 'Sturmbringer' auszulösen und die Abklingzeit Eurer Fähigkeit 'Sturmschlag' zurückzusetzen.
description_blz.en_GB: Your Feral Spirits' attacks have a 20% chance to trigger Stormbringer, resetting the cooldown of your Stormstrike.

description_blz.ko_KR: 야수 정령이 공격 시 20%의 확률로 폭풍인도자를 발동시켜, 폭풍의 일격의 재사용 대기시간을 초기화시킵니다.
